{"tid":591091,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[捕捉他] 40歲杜奧巴踢埋今季掛靴","createTime":"2018-03-13T08:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T14:54:07.000Z","uid":29625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de320833bed119eea4445d0e8a5a80b76ae780c5","tid":591091,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"剛度過40歲生日的杜奧巴宣佈，為鳳凰城Phoenix Rising完成今季美國足球聯盟(USL)賽事後，將正式高掛球靴。<br />\n<br />\n剛在周日40歲生日的杜奧巴將出戰2018年USL球季，但同時亦是他最後一季，「我很遲才展開頂級聯賽生涯，但我很享受比賽，很高興可與眾多年青球員一起，把我的經驗傳授給他們，但我已經40歲，這將是最後一季。」<br />\n<br />\n杜奧巴1998年在勒芒展開球員生涯，2004年加盟車路士踏上顛峰，兩次效力射入超過150球，贏得4次英超冠軍及1次歐聯冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n對於回到他曾效力的馬賽擔任其他職位，杜奧巴說︰「我會看看他們給我甚麼，我一直樂意效勞，馬賽近年發展得很好，以年青球員建立球隊，並保住三甲位置，做得十分出色。」同時間杜奧巴的兒子亦已展開球員之路，加入甘岡青年軍。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=RRFyPJExOFzaatkg3WeVH4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=94118e6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"98d536965ccefcde0bc9db1e4d18f40cf0ff29d1","tid":591091,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8f84f9e22e22bd6d62f59bc9472918b5eb05c6","tid":591091,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:54:07.000Z","msg":"即刻wiki下佢發覺多左個狗字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/225404_26674383b8019b5be5b996391c4dd1b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F225404_26674383b8019b5be5b996391c4dd1b1.png&h=7fb25362&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}